TY  - JOUR
AU  - Repullo, Rafael
T1  - The Core of an Economy with Transaction Costs
PY  - 1988
Y1  - 1988/07/01
DO  - 10.2307/2297394
JO  - The Review of Economic Studies
JA  - Rev Econ Stud
VL  - 55
IS  - 3
SP  - 447
EP  - 458
SN  - 0034-6527
AB  - This paper defines a new concept of the core for an economy with transaction costs, and uses this concept to prove a limit theorem for sequences of replica economies. In this way it provides a rationale for a definition of equilibrium in which agents face a sequence of budget constraints. Since economies with incomplete markets are special cases of economies with transaction costs, the limit theorem also provides a rationale for Radner's equilibrium of plans, prices, and price expectations.
Y2  - 3/25/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.2307/2297394
ER  - 



